OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWindy with a scattering of
OL,6,Fshowers at first, these tending to
OL,7,Fbecome lighter and isolated into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Some bright or sunny spells
OL,9,Fat times, especially in the east.
OL,10,FWinds gradually easing later.
OL,11,FTemperatures near average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FGenerally dry with some clear
OL,14,Fspells at first, but cloud thickening
OL,15,Ffrom the west towards midnight,
OL,16,Fbringing some patchy rain and drizzle
OL,17,Feastwards through the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
